  "title": "Project Engineer",
  "description": "<p>Job Description &amp; Requirements</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Manage, design, develop, create and maintain various scale construction projects in a safe, timely manner</li>\n  <li>Liaise with Clients, Consultants, and Authorities on the project status from time to time.</li>\n  <li>Carry out technical and feasibility studies for technical specifications</li>\n  <li>Assess potential risks, materials and costs and provide advice to resolve any emerging problems/deficiencies</li>\n  <li>Project implementation involving all authorities applications/ submissions, work procedures</li>\n  <li>Monitor progress and compile reports on project status</li>\n  <li>Any other ad-hoc tasks assigned</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Possess a recognized Degree/Diploma in Civil Engineering or equivalent.</li>\n  <li>Minimum 3 years of relevant experience</li>\n  <li>Prior working experience in civil engineering will be an advantage.</li>\n  <li>Proficiency in site layout, grading, utility design, erosion control, regulatory approvals etc.</li>\n  <li>Class 3 Driving License preferred.</li>\n</ul>",
