    "description": "<p>Founded in Year 1986, Shingda is one of the few local construction companies that specialize in the development of utilities main. Our core services centered on the design, construction and modification of Portable Water, NEWater, Industrial Water, Raw Water, Sewer and Gas pipelines.</p>  <p>Our clienteles include the Public Utilities Board of Singapore, Changi Airport Group and the Defence Science & Technology Agency.</p>  <p>Shingda is accredited with ISO 9001:2000, ISO 14001:2004 and OHSAS 18001:1999 and is registered with Building Construction Authority (BCA) under the Workhead of Cable / Pipe Laying & Road Reinstatement (CR07) and Civil Engineering Works (CW02). Align with our entrenched belief in business excellence, Shingda had been actively involved in the business excellence movement and is one of the few construction firms that have been accredited the prestigious Singapore Quality Class Star and Singapore Innovation Class.</p>  <p>Singapore is fast becoming a focal centre for the water industry, with activities spanning the entire value chain of construction, design, operation and R&D. This, coupled with the government initiatives and emphasis on water conservation, has translated to more business opportunities for Shingda. Moving forward, Shingda is determined to further develop and enhance its core competencies to improve its market position in the total market volume with its emphasis on quality and professionalism.</p> ",
